		"name": "Functional test - voucher registration",
		"description": "Test to verify the functionality of the process of registering new vouchers in the API.\n\nBased on the user story:  \n**As** an EBAC-SHOP admin  \n**I want** create a voucher service  \n**To** be able to list and register vouchers\n\n**Business rules:**\n\n- You must register the vouchers with the mandatory fields below:\n    \n    - Voucher code\n        \n    - Value\n        \n    - Discount type\n        \n    - Description\n        \n- Coupon name cannot be repeated\n    \n\n**Test mindmap**\n\n<img src=\"https://content.pstmn.io/68f7e47e-b566-4a1f-9a3c-e38bb20a136e/VVMtMDAwMy5wbmc=\">\n\n**Expected results:**\n\n- Successful registration of new voucher\n    \n- Do not allow registration of a voucher with an existing name.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "22996953"
	},
